it's so important.

00:55:40.232 --> 00:55:41.690
And there have been
many times when

00:55:41.690 --> 00:55:42.890
I've been talking to my
husband and I'm like,

00:55:42.890 --> 00:55:43.750
I'm on my way therapy.

00:55:43.750 --> 00:55:44.480
I nothing to say.

00:55:44.480 --> 00:55:46.666
And then I leave like, that was
the best session I've ever had.

00:55:46.666 --> 00:55:47.900
CATHERINE BIRNDORF: It's better
when you have nothing to say.

00:55:47.900 --> 00:55:48.560
